										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Have you used AI image generators yet? I‚Äôve played around with a few and found them both incredible and incredibly frustrating. The first version I get is like 95% correct. Then I ask for a little tweak, and it throws the whole thing out of whack.</p>
<p>I know people have had success with these platforms, and I wanted to know how. So I asked several content, design, and marketing pros how they use AI to help create quality images.</p>
<p>They shared a bunch of really good beginner tips that‚Äôll help AI-design newbies, and some advanced tactics for people who‚Äôve tinkered with these tools a lot already. They also opened my eyes to several AI tools I‚Äôd never heard of, and even one website that‚Äôs a collection of hundreds of open-source models you can use.</p>
<p>I&#8217;ve documented all their tips, processes, and platform suggestions here so that you can try them too.</p>
