<div id="ai-tools-for-content-creation"></div>
<h2>AI tools for content creation</h2>
<p>Now, using<a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/02/25/ai-content-generators"> AI tools to create your content</a> start to finish isn‚Äôt the best strategy. Especially because it can impact your brand‚Äôs<a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/topical-authority"> authority</a> and relationship with your audience, but you should definitely use AI tools for productivity gains throughout the content creation process‚Äîwhether it‚Äôs brainstorming, outlining, or even reviewing for tone. Just be sure to play an active role and review everything.</p>
<h3>1. Jasper</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.jasper.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jasper</a> is a generative AI tool that helps you create marketing copy, including <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2015/02/09/how-to-write-a-blog-post">blog posts</a>, product descriptions, landing pages, social captions, and more. This AI tool uses advanced large language models (LLMs) purpose-built for writing copy, which makes the output stronger than some other <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/chatgpt-alternatives">alternatives</a>. Plus, you can input examples so that Jasper learns your brand voice and can replicate it as it writes.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-jasper.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Jasper" width="937" height="468" class="aligncenter wp-image-93206 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-jasper.webp 937w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-jasper-480x240.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 937px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.jasper.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>However, this better output comes with a cost. Jasper is pricier than a lot of other options, so make sure it works for your budget before testing it out.</p>
<p><strong>Jasper pricing:</strong> <a href="https://www.jasper.ai/pricing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jasper‚Äôs Creator plan</a> costs $39 per month.</p>
<h3><strong></strong>2. Copy.ai</h3>
<p><a href="http://copy.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Copy.ai</a> is an <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ai-copywriting-tools">AI copywriting assistant</a> that can produce nearly any type of copy, but it excels particularly in creating short-form content, such as <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/instagram-ad-copy">social captions</a>, product descriptions, and <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/07/21/promotional-email-examples">marketing emails</a>. The tool is straightforward and easy to use, so you can get lots of options quickly.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-copy-ai.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Copy ai" width="873" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-93207 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-copy-ai.webp 873w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-copy-ai-480x330.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 873px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.copy.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>Copy.ai offers robust workflow features, but other tools give you more control over tone.</p>
<p><strong>Copy.ai pricing:</strong> Copy.ai offers a <a href="https://www.copy.ai/prices" target="_blank" rel="noopener">basic free plan</a>, and its paid plans start at $49 per month.</p>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f6a8.png" alt="üö®" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <strong>Need to catch up on AI tools and uses?</strong> Download the <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/resources/emergency-ai-guide?cid=Web_Any_BlogInContent_PPC_AIMarketing_Download">Emergency Guide to AI in Marketing</a></p>
<div id="ai-tools-for-scheduling-and-calendar-management"></div>
<h2>AI tools for scheduling and calendar management</h2>
<p>Managing your calendar takes time, from scheduling meetings to reviewing your day to moving things around when an unexpected doctor‚Äôs appointment or client call takes precedence. (Seriously, why is it still so annoying to move appointments in the Google Calendar app?)</p>
<p>Here are a few tools to make it all easier.</p>
<h3>3. Clockwise</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.getclockwise.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Clockwise</a> uses AI to automatically optimize your calendar by finding the best times for meetings, eliminating the back-and-forth. It also blocks out time for prep and debriefing based on your own settings. It even protects dedicated focus time to ensure you can get everything done in your day.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-clockwise.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Clockwise" width="937" height="529" class="aligncenter wp-image-93208 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-clockwise.webp 937w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-clockwise-480x271.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 937px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.getclockwise.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>Another key thing here is that Clockwise focuses on team-wide time management, not just individual calendars. That‚Äôs a bonus if you‚Äôre looking to improve the way your department, or even your business, manages scheduling.</p>
<p>Make note that while Clockwise integrates with Google Calendar, it has limited support for Microsoft users at this time.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Clockwise<a href="https://www.getclockwise.com/pricing" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> offers a free plan</a>, and its paid plans start at $6.75 per month.</p>
<h3>4. Motion</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.usemotion.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Motion</a> offers AI-powered scheduling that it blends with task management. Motion allows you to input your to-do list as well as link your calendar, so that the AI tool has the ability to consider your time in meetings as well as your time for tasks.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-motion.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Motion" width="662" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-93209 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-motion.webp 662w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-motion-480x435.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 662px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.usemotion.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></p>
<p>According to the Motion team, that‚Äôs how the tool organizes your day dynamically based on priority.</p>
<p>This is a huge pro in automatically prioritizing tasks, in addition to the same time-savings you get by eliminating manual meeting planning. But be aware that this automated prioritizing can feel too restrictive for some. Still, it‚Äôs worth testing out.</p>
<p><strong>Motion pricing:</strong> <a href="https://www.getclockwise.com/pricing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Motion pricing</a> starts at $19 per seat, billed monthly.</p>
<div id="ai-tools-for-more-productive-meetings"></div>
<h2>AI tools for more productive meetings</h2>
<p>This meeting could have been an email! How often do you wish your meetings were more useful and concise? These AI tools will help you make that dream a reality.</p>
<h3><strong></strong>5. Otter.ai</h3>
<p><a href="http://otter.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Otter.ai</a> is an AI tool that provides real-time transcription, summaries, and highlights of meetings. It integrates with Zoom, Microsoft Teams, and Google Meet, so you‚Äôre covered regardless of the platform your company uses.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-otter.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Otter ai" width="937" height="546" class="aligncenter wp-image-93210 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-otter.webp 937w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-otter-480x280.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 937px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://otter.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>Unlike some other meeting tools, you can edit Otter.ai‚Äôs transcription live to ensure accuracy. This is especially important because the transcriptions are not only searchable, but you can use its chatbot to get information from previous meetings. Otter.ai is a great tool for collaboration and keeping your team all on the same page‚Äîor for double-checking customer requests before following up.</p>
<p><strong>Otter.ai pricing:</strong> <a href="http://otter.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Otter.ai/pricing</a> offers a free Basic plan, with its Pro plan starting at $8.33 per month.</p>
<h3>6. Scribbl</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.scribbl.co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Scribbl</a> is a super simple, lightweight tool if you‚Äôre mainly looking to capture meeting transcripts. The interface is straightforward, and it‚Äôs free to get started for up to 15 meetings per month.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-scribble.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Scribbl" width="637" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-93211 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-scribble.webp 637w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-scribble-480x452.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 637px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.scribbl.co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>Scribbl automatically shares transcripts with meeting attendees or other designated recipients, and it integrates with common tools like Google Drive, Slack, and HubSpot. But keep in mind that other than this, the tool offers minimal advanced features.</p>
<p><strong>Scribbl pricing:</strong> Scribbl offers a<a href="https://www.scribbl.co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> free Lite plan</a>, and its paid plans start at $13 per month.</p>
<div id="ai-tools-to-streamline-your-emails"></div>
<h2>AI tools to streamline your emails</h2>
<p>I‚Äôll be honest: I‚Äôve given up on ever reaching inbox zero. But I still need to apply some order to all the emails if I want to avoid devolving into chaos and ensure I‚Äôm catching all the important messages. Setting up this organization manually is time-consuming, and worse, it‚Äôs easy to lose your progress and slip out of it. That‚Äôs why you need to try a tool to streamline your emails if you‚Äôre looking to use AI for productivity.</p>
<h3>7. Gemini for Gmail</h3>
<p>Using AI tools that are native to your email system is a win because they‚Äôre automatically integrated. That‚Äôs why if you‚Äôre already a Google Workspace user, consider testing out <a href="https://gemini.google.com/app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gemini</a> for Gmail. Gemini helps you draft replies, summarize lengthy email threads, search for information in your inbox, get information from your Google calendar, find Google Drive files, and more.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-gemini.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Gemini" width="937" height="581" class="aligncenter wp-image-93212 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-gemini.webp 937w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-gemini-480x298.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 937px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>Unfortunately, this is only available for Gmail users, and it‚Äôs most effective if you‚Äôre a full Google Workspace user.</p>
<p><strong>Google Gemini pricing:</strong> You can use the basic version of Google Gemini for free or get the Pro version for $19.99 per month.</p>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f44b.png" alt="üëã" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <strong>Make email easier!</strong> Get <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/resources/email-examples-and-templates?cid=Web_Any_InContentTextLink_Email_EmailTemplates_Download&amp;itm_source=wordstream&amp;itm_medium=blog&amp;itm_campaign=incontent_links">The Complete Email Marketing Toolkit: Free Email Templates, Subject Lines, and Tips</a></p>
<h3>8. Superhuman</h3>
<p><a href="https://superhuman.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Superhuman</a> uses AI-backed shortcuts and automations to help you organize your inbox and spend less time getting through more emails. Sounds great, right?</p>
<p>The tool labels and sorts emails so that you can quickly skim your inbox for the most important ones. Plus, Superhuman will automatically archive marketing emails, especially cold pitches. Superhuman will even help you schedule meetings in one click, draft replies, and more.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-superhuman.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Superhuman" width="937" height="531" class="aligncenter wp-image-93213 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-superhuman.webp 937w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-superhuman-480x272.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 937px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://superhuman.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>The one downside to this AI productivity tool is that it is pretty pricy compared to other options in this category</p>
<p><strong>Superhuman pricing:</strong> <a href="https://superhuman.com/pricing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Superhuman pricing plans</a> start at $25 per month.</p>
<div id="ai-tools-for-more-efficient-research"></div>
<h2>AI tools for more efficient research</h2>
<p>You want the most trustworthy sources for your work. But it‚Äôs so easy to get caught up in research rabbit holes that waste time and lead you to dead ends. Here are a couple of tools to help make research more efficient, allowing you to spend the most time on the best sources.</p>
<h3>9. Genei</h3>
<p>Explicitly designed for researchers and writers,<a href="https://www.genei.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> Genei</a> instantly summarizes research papers, web pages, and long articles. The platform allows you to search and select articles to review and summarize, and it also supports blog post drafting if you‚Äôre looking for a place to get started.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-genei2.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Genei" width="937" height="444" class="aligncenter wp-image-93215 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-genei2.webp 937w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-genei2-480x227.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 937px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.genei.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>Another benefit of Genei is that it includes citations, allowing you to access your sources directly for follow-ups.</p>
<p><strong>Genei pricing:</strong> Genei <a href="https://www.genei.io/pricing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">lists its pricing</a> in British pounds, but the lowest tier plan costs roughly $13.45 USD.</p>
<h3>10. Glasp</h3>
<p><a href="https://glasp.co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Glasp</a> is a browser add-on that lets you easily highlight and save web content, generating summaries and personal knowledge banks while you browse and read on your own. You can use the chat function to search your notes and summaries, and you can even export your notes files to upload elsewhere or share with your team. Glasp has similar functionality for summarizing videos.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-glasp.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from glasp" width="937" height="528" class="aligncenter wp-image-93216 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-glasp.webp 937w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-glasp-480x270.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 937px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://glasp.co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>The downside is that Glasp isn‚Äôt intended for deep research, so that‚Äôs something to be aware of as you‚Äôre testing it out.</p>
<p><strong>Glasp pricing:</strong> <a href="https://glasp.co/pricing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Glasp has a free plan</a>, and its paid plans start at $10 per month.</p>
<div id="ai-tools-for-automating-tasks-and-workflows"></div>
<h2>AI tools for automating tasks and workflows</h2>
<p>One of the best ways to<a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency"> use AI tools</a> for productivity is to automate repetitive, time-consuming tasks. The setup might take some time and testing, but letting the tasks run without your intervention frees up your creative energy for other essential tasks.</p>
<h3>11. Zapier AI</h3>
<p><a href="https://zapier.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zapier</a> is essentially a middleman that can create connections between thousands of digital platforms and apps. It acts like an intermediary, allowing two apps to work together. For example, if you need items from a Typeform submission to be converted into lines on a Google Sheet or to add Google Calendar events to a Notion page, Zapier can help.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-zapier.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Zapier" width="798" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-93217 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-zapier.webp 798w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-zapier-480x361.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 798px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em>An example of a Zap, Zapier‚Äôs name for a connection between apps.</em></p>
<p>There are numerous templates and AI-powered suggestions, but in some cases, these automations‚Äîcalled zaps‚Äîcan become quite complex and require trial and error to set up..</p>
<p><strong>Zapier pricing:</strong><a href="https://zapier.com/pricing" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> Zapier offers several pricing plans</a> tailored to your use case, with free options available. The paid version for creating Zaps starts at $19.99 per month.</p>
<h3>12. Bardeen</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.bardeen.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bardeen</a> is a tool built specifically for go-to-market teams. It automates repetitive browser tasks using AI and pre-built playbooks, and it‚Äôs installed directly into your browser for easy integration with everyday tasks, such as pulling data from your CRM or <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/11/03/lead-nurturing">sending an automated email to a lead</a> in Outlook.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-bardeen.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Bardeen" width="963" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-93218 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-bardeen.webp 963w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-bardeen-480x299.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 963px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.bardeen.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>Bardeen lets you create and reuse workflows. Once it&#8217;s set up, you can apply your workflow to new sales tasks quickly.</p>
<p><strong>Bardeen pricing:</strong> <a href="https://www.bardeen.ai/pricing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bardeen pricing</a> starts at $99 per month.</p>
<div id="ai-tools-for-maintaining-productivity-gains"></div>
<h2>AI tools for maintaining productivity gains</h2>
<p>Once you‚Äôve taken the time to test out and implement some AI tools to make your workday more productive, you want to make sure you can stick to it. Here are AI tools to help you maintain these productivity gains‚Äîstay on track, ensure everything is organized, and keep your time and attention free to focus on bigger-picture strategy.</p>
<h3>13. ChatGPT (OpenAI)</h3>
<p><a href="http://chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ChatGPT</a> is one of the most well-known and widely used AI solutions. The chat-based tool can assist with a wide range of tasks, including writing, coding, brainstorming, and<a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/09/05/chatgpt-seo"> SEO</a>. It‚Äôs incredibly versatile, and while you‚Äôre focusing on using AI for productivity, it‚Äôs worth exploring how ChatGPT can also speed up your other tasks in your day-to-day routine.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-chatgpt-1.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Chatgpt" width="866" height="467" class="aligncenter wp-image-93220 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-chatgpt-1.webp 866w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-chatgpt-1-480x259.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 866px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>ChatGPT, like other chat-based tools, works by feeding it prompts. We‚Äôve curated a<a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/05/08/chatgpt-prompts"> list of prompts</a> you can try to get started.</p>
<p><strong>ChatGPT pricing: </strong>ChatGPT offers a robust free version that anyone can use, while its paid subscriptions start at $20 per month.</p>
<h3>14. Notion AI</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.notion.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Notion AI</a> is a workspace that can automatically generate content inside Notion pages‚Äîfrom meeting notes to action items‚Äîand allows you to search your knowledge base. It also helps build workflows within Notion, for example, creating pages, task trackers, and calendars for a new product or marketing campaign.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-notion.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Notion" width="688" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-93221 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-notion.webp 688w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-notion-480x419.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 688px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.notion.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<p>This is great if you‚Äôre already a Notion user. And if you‚Äôre looking for a solution for documentation creation, storage, and access, then Notion could be a great solution.</p>
<p><strong>Notion pricing:</strong> <a href="https://www.notion.com/pricing">Notion has a free plan</a>, and its paid plans start at $10 per month.</p>
<h3><strong></strong>15. Reclaim.ai</h3>
<p>Now, this is similar to the calendar tools, but we‚Äôre putting it here because of its singular mission: <a href="http://reclaim.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Reclaim.ai </a>¬†automatically blocks time for habits, tasks, and meetings based on your goals and availability. And even better, Reclaim will help you track your time so that you can review your patterns‚Äîand stay honest and accountable.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-reclaim.webp" alt="AI productivity tools - screenshot from Reclaim" width="879" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-93222 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-reclaim.webp 879w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ai-productivity-tools-wordstream-reclaim-480x328.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 879px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="http://reclaim.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<p>When you‚Äôre automating and leveraging AI tools to get more productive, you don‚Äôt want to lose control over those newly gained work blocks. The only drawback to note here is that, at least for now, Reclaim.ai only integrates with Google Calendar.</p>
<p><strong>Reclaim pricing:</strong> You can use Reclaim‚Äôs Lite plan for free, and the paid plans start at $8 per month.</p>
<h2>Start using these AI tools for productivity</h2>
<p>You‚Äôre busy, and sometimes it feels like you‚Äôre too busy to start testing out new workflows or tools when you need to get things done. But if you can invest a little time to stand up one AI productivity tool, it‚Äôll free up enough time to try another, and possibly another. Then, all of a sudden, you have lots of time back in your day.</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ai-productivity-tools">15 AI Productivity Tools We Love</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
